title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 43-2.14 - Enrollment of providers
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 43-2.14 - Enrollment of providers

State Regulations

The department will contract with or enter into provider agreements with providers, including providers of related laboratory and ancillary services, which demonstrate that they are qualified to provide prescription drugs. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10
§§
43-2.14

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
